TestOuterErrorVarVisibleAfterInnerHandlerCloses
/ After the inner error.handle scope closes, the outer recovery body's %!error% restores to the outer caught error via LIFO AsyncLocal scope. Reuses OuterRecoveryWithInnerThrow which sets %outerSeenAfterInner% AFTER its inner handler closes.
- throw error "outer-boom", on error call OuterRecoveryWithInnerThrow
- assert %outerSeenAfterInner% equals "outer-boom"
